title: Aaron Rodgers Throws Amazing 50-Yard Hail Mary Pass To Randall Cobb During Playoff Game Giants
text:
Aaron Rodgers gonna Aaron Rodgers. 
Before halftime, the Green Bay Packers QB converted a 50-yard hail mary TD pass to Randall Cobb because of a lapse in the Giants defense. 
Cobb looked like he pushed off but it’s still amazing.
